ygData.messageBody:
Well sorry to say but there are no human npc's in faydwer we are elves.
Once you zone through to greater faydark. Hang a left and hug the zone
wall be careful of wandering guards because they really like to bash
things =)

Klaen
The Tree Hugging Ranger
